  "title": "Introduction to Basic Chords",
  "lessonText": "In this lesson, you'll learn the foundational chords that will help you play your first songs.",
  "data": {
    "content": "## Key Points\n- Chords are the building blocks of songs.\n- Start with basic chords: C, G, D, and Em.\n- Practice transitioning between chords smoothly.\n- Use a metronome to keep time.\n- Aim for clarity in each chord sound."
  }
}
